# ==================================
# Tikkie / iDEAL Payment Integration
# ==================================
# Tikkie is ABN AMRO's payment request service using iDEAL.
# Without these settings, the app runs in DEMO mode (mock payment URLs).
#
# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Register at https://developer.abnamro.com/
# 2. Create an app and subscribe to the Tikkie API
# 3. Get your API Key (Consumer Key) and generate an App Token
# 4. For production: Link your ABN AMRO business account
#
# TIKKIE_API_KEY=your-consumer-key-here
# TIKKIE_APP_TOKEN=your-app-token-here
# TIKKIE_SANDBOX=true  # Set to false for production
